title: Kiss it Goodbye
itunes:title: Kiss it Goodbye
description:
If you’re going to reach your destiny, you have to learn to kiss the negative things goodbye. There are people and opportunities that were assigned to your past but are not assigned to your future. It’s time to allow God to heal the wounds of the past so you can move into the destiny He has for you.To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
